    ##If you’re arriving in the UK before 3pm (UK time) on 23 April 2025

    You do not need an ETA if you will not pass through UK border control. 

    All of the following must apply:

    * you booked and paid for your journey to the UK before 3pm (UK time) on 12 March 2025
    * you’re arriving in the UK before 3pm (UK time) on 23 April 2025
    * you meet the [Standard Visitor visa](/standard-visitor) eligibility requirements

    You should bring evidence of your onward journey, such as a ticket to your destination.

    %You may want to apply for a [transit visa](/transit-visa) instead if you have a criminal record or you’ve previously been refused entry into the UK.
